    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Almohadin: escape from the basement</strong> <strong>(AEFTB) </strong>是一款充满多彩视觉效果和弹幕动作的独立快节奏2D精准平台游戏。面对一个故事丰富的卡通冒险，灵感来自于困难的复古横版卷轴街机游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>地下室藏有许多秘密。Almohadin 必须冒险并揭开它们才能到达外面的世界。加入他的冒险吧！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras/dc5341686b53d1551ba5eb1faa26aeea.avif?t=1768310336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras_big/dc5341686b53d1551ba5eb1faa26aeea.avif?t=1768310336 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一系列难度递增的关卡等待着你，以及视觉小说的叙事方式，让你沉浸在 Almohadin 的故事中——一个魔法般活过来的枕头，决定逃离地下室。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras/0539b47134108f18a4a23f93189ecac8.avif?t=1768310336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras_big/0539b47134108f18a4a23f93189ecac8.avif?t=1768310336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存与战斗！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>头目</strong> - 这些强大的个体将竭尽全力试图杀死你。保卫自己！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>救援</strong> - 数百名对象被囚禁在地下室。做出改变，拯救他们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>屠杀</strong> - 消灭所有挡路的怪物。净化被侵扰的区域。恢复和平！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>机制</strong> - 一路上，你会发现许多变得更强大的方法：增强你移动能力的 alfajores、武器、传送药丸、帮助你飞行的豆子罐头（我不会解释怎么做……）、无敌药水，还有更多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras/04e000cf9fb7c0f57f44f8cedc7ccf66.avif?t=1768310336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras_big/04e000cf9fb7c0f57f44f8cedc7ccf66.avif?t=1768310336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这些关卡中，你必须尽可能快地获胜。与其他玩家竞争，看看谁是最快的逃脱者。有些关卡极其困难！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras/b975cfa34d5aa0ecd3c71ecdf599d1e2.avif?t=1768310336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157360/extras_big/b975cfa34d5aa0ecd3c71ecdf599d1e2.avif?t=1768310336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>再次奔跑……</i></p>",
